{"tid":1461513,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"如何在人山人海情況下上網","createTime":"2019-08-13T08:05:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T10:54:46.000Z","uid":42691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"208f980901301429d332d201cb58bb9f6f25fc44","tid":1461513,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:05:09.000Z","msg":"4G=跑車 3G=電單車 2G=行路<br />\n<br />\n視乎需要去設定較<br />\n4G 開live 高清片<br />\n3G 睇片 睇圖<br />\n2G 純文字訊息 TG Whatsapp<br />\n<br />\n上到網就入黎同我開分身fb ac<br />\n離開連登 咪撚再圍爐 <br />\n<br />\n我地需要網絡大軍做實事<br />\n有大量藍絲活在資訊封閉既井底需要我地拯救<br />\n有心地唔差既藍絲需要被拉攏<br />\n有極端藍絲言論需要被大家推上TOP <br />\n從而嚇走理性藍絲(以藍制藍)<br />\n<br />\n申請完請加<br />\nZhong kwok wan<br />\nZhang Simon<br />\n入面既朋友<br />\n唔好貪心一次過加太多人 否則會要求提供電話<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\n入面有各樣傳送門<br />\n請離開連登，離開同溫層。連登太多頭腦，欠缺手腳。全部同我入黎申請分身ac！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1439811\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1439811</a></span>"},{"pid":"d318c18dbd2a3a85a8df5cedfcbfc6336e0c5ee8","tid":1461513,"uid":294974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:27:36.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得講得啱，唔該睇睇同幫推唔該<br />\np牌仔嘅野冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(話我鬼都要講㗎喇)佔機場唔係無撚敵㗎，屌<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dDbQKT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dDbQKT</a>"},{"pid":"0a5185750c0e34d6db5ec12bf1b9322fd64c2ee0","tid":1461513,"uid":242734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:01:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"574906a13e57dcd117da2e70d2d0c641b0a30cec","tid":1461513,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:09:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a71356c8139b390e1d08ab86140d5749fdf72bb1","tid":146151